      "start": 45.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 55.84000015258789,
      "text": "I need every second of every sip, make it strong",
      "start": 50.380001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 63.7599983215332,
      "text": "I need a blackout without you, I need a blackout",
      "start": 55.900001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 75.76000213623047,
      "text": "So I can't remember how you used to make it drop for me",
      "start": 64.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 84.62000274658203,
      "text": "Spend that cash, looking so good, it's ecstasy",
      "start": 76.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 90.9000015258789,
      "text": "I'm missing it, I don't wanna remember it all",
      "start": 84.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 94.9000015258789,
      "text": "I need a blackout, I need a blackout",
      "start": 90.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 99.66000366210938,
      "text": "Every time I think about how you left me here",
      "start": 94.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 104.13999938964844,
      "text": "I got no life now, there's no life now",
      "start": 99.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 109.16000366210938,
      "text": "Just thinking about that money and taking it away",
      "start": 104.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 117.22000122070312,
      "text": "I need you more than you need me, that's what I feel",
      "start": 109.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 125.31999969482422,
      "text": "I need you more than you needed me",
      "start": 118.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 131.5,
      "text": "I need a blackout, I need a blackout",
      "start": 126.5
    },
    {
      "end": 136.17999267578125,
      "text": "There's no time to remember it anyway",
      "start": 131.5
    },
    {
      "end": 140.66000366210938,
      "text": "Give me a blackout, and just a blackout",
      "start": 136.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 143.67999267578125,
      "text": "What do you got on tab? What drugs you got?",
      "start": 140.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 145.89999389648438,
      "text": "What can you give to me today?",
      "start": 143.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 148.77999877929688,
      "text": "Cause I don't wanna remember you",
      "start": 146.24000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 151.74000549316406,
      "text": "I don't wanna remember how good you were at night",
      "start": 148.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 155.32000732421875,
      "text": "Done all that, did everything right, girl",
      "start": 151.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 161.75999450683594,
      "text": "I don't wanna remember all the times you said you were mine",
      "start": 155.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 163.6999969482422,
      "text": "That we were forever",
      "start": 161.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 169.27999877929688,
      "text": "I need a blackout, I need a fucking blackout",
      "start": 163.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 175.60000610351562,
      "text": "For you guys, I can't remember anything but",
      "start": 169.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 178.25999450683594,
      "text": "The moments you gave",
      "start": 175.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 181.94000244140625,
      "text": "Your sexual warnings",
      "start": 178.5
    },
    {
      "end": 186.6999969482422,
      "text": "Blacked out drunk, I caught you up",
      "start": 182.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 190.72000122070312,
      "text": "And you tell me to go get low",
      "start": 186.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 197.1199951171875,
      "text": "I'm already low, I wish that you'd ever see me",
